Project Dependency Graph

Dependency Tree

  • org.jmxtrans.jmxtrans2:jmxtrans2-output-writers:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT
    JMXTrans - output writers

    Description: Implementation of OutputWriters for a number of backends. Those are kept outside of jmxtrans-core as they do bring additional dependencies in some cases and we want to strongly enforce that no code in jmxtrans-core depends on specific OutputWriter.

    URL: http://www.jmxtrans.org/jmxtrans2/jmxtrans2-output-writers

    Project License: MIT License

    • com.google.code.findbugs:jsr305:jar:3.0.0 (compile)

      Project License: The Apache Software License, Version 2.0

    • org.jmxtrans.jmxtrans2:jmxtrans2-core:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT (compile)
      JMXTrans - core

      Description: Core functionality of JmxTrans is found here. Integration with specific runtime environment is kept outside this module (agent, spring, standalone, ...), but if you just want some code to help you easily query JMX beans, this is what you need.

      URL: http://www.jmxtrans.org/jmxtrans2/jmxtrans2-core

      Project License: MIT License

    • org.jmxtrans.jmxtrans2:jmxtrans2-utils:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT (compile)
      JMXTrans - utils

      Description: Utilities which have no direct connections with JmxTrans. All classes found in this module could potentially be reused by other projects. Some duplicate functionality already found in standard libraries like Guava, but as we want to keep external dependencies to a bare minimum, we have to reimplement them.

      URL: http://www.jmxtrans.org/jmxtrans2/jmxtrans2-utils

      Project License: MIT License
